rows.label: qev085904_MSG0001
rows.name: And after we went to all that trouble...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085904_MSG0002
rows.name: I never imagined it couldn't be done.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085904_MSG0003
rows.name:
Just because our tech can't handle it
doesn't make it impossible.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085904_MSG0004
rows.name:
I met a Ma-non craftsman a while back
who works with rare minerals.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085904_MSG0005
rows.name: He's not cheap, but he's good. Why don't I introduce you?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085904_MSG0008
rows.name:
I know you've been working hard
to help out one of my crew, Lin.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085904_MSG0011
rows.name: How about letting me join in the fun from here?[ST:wait ]
